{"tid":1955870,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好再鬥黃啦，好嘛！？連中立撚都變埋藍啦","createTime":"2020-04-02T19:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T11:10:07.000Z","uid":18552,"like":21,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"29db276baab83e985f4285617259eaebd51592ac","tid":1955870,"uid":18552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T19:04:13.000Z","msg":"嗰個人就係我老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由14年我就叫佢登記做選民<br />\n去到19年底 佢都話政治野唔關佢事 <br />\n佢中立唔會投票<br />\n佢身邊d 朋友多數都係藍絲<br />\n依排因為疫程 佢都無工開<br />\n點知佢就日日都係睇youtube 睇藍怡<br />\n仲話佢講嘅野好有道理<br />\n仲話要立即做登記做選民<br />\n我全家人聽到都：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直以黎 我老豆都話自己係中立<br />\n估唔到d濕鳩kol真係會有影響力咖<br />\n<br />\n  所以大家真係唔好要內鬥<br />\n大家一齊諗下點樣去令到大家團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！<br />\n依個唔係一個口號<br />\n香港要改變 我地仲需要大家一分力<br />\n我地大家都要一齊進步！<br />\n<br />\n明嘅就明啦 我廢up完了 <br />\n希望可以訓得著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4247c73d333ed3adff520fa37d570e905c3959f5","tid":1955870,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T19:05:04.000Z","msg":"藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ee2d18a2e70f8e75226a8965b35ca11354df59","tid":1955870,"uid":18552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4247c73d333ed3adff520fa37d570e905c3959f5","tid":1955870,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T19:05:04.000Z","msg":"藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T19:06:34.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係會有一班中立撚會表態係藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f57f6cc97a36a227ee732fce06fb6d28472a68","tid":1955870,"uid":2607,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T19:08:3